The paper deals with the problem of inferring the input and hidden variables of a stochastic multi-layer neural network, which involves signal recovery via deep generative prior models, multi-task and mixed regression, and learning certain classes of two-layer neural networks. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Information Theory (cs.IT), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), Signal Processing (cs.SI), and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI).
